comment._content: "Gladstone Flash," A-20G serial 43-21426, had previously served with the 387th Bomb Squadron, 312th BG as "Eloise" (tail letter A).

comment._content: My father was part of the aircrew for this aircraft. Philipines and/or New Guinea. A gunner.
